channel.title: ~PwnScape V1[317]-requesting summoning models~
channel.description:
hello and welcome to my development thread, this [u]is not[/u] delta, this is a blank czar source. [b]Will this be released?[/b] yes this will be released (open source) there is not an exact date as to when it will be released. [b]Programming experience[/b] I have been Programming RSPS's for about almost half a year now i believe? [b]What type of server will this be?[/b] this will be more Pk driven, with mini games and a good economy (if all goes as planned) [b]Is there a blog open?[/b] yes, but i need permission to post a link. [b]Will there be beta testing?[/b] Of course, i will chose 5 people i know can find bugs and faults in my server that i will try at my best to fix. [b]Will this be hosted?[/b] Yes it will, but not for a while.
